snippet.title: Johnny Depp And Amber Heard's Divorce Case Ends!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s messy divorce has quickly come to an end! They settled in court on August 16 after Amber dropped the domestic violence restraining order against her ex.
Media reports claim Johnny paid Amber about $7 million, which included her attorney fees. A recent statement released by the former read: “Our relationship was intensely passionate and at times volatile, but always bound by love… Neither party has made false accusations for financial gains.”

Watch the video and don’t forget to subscribe to our YouTube Channel!
